OL,3,CReform council leader defends spending
OL,4,C#75k putting up Union flags
OL,6,FReform UK will spend #75,000 putting
OL,7,Fup 150 Union flags across
OL,8,FNottinghamshire in a bid to
OL,9,F"strengthen community spirit".
OL,11,FOpposition parties say the money could
OL,12,Fhave been spent on other council
OL,13,Fservices - but Reform says its new
OL,14,Fbanner locations will also be used to
OL,15,Fsupport events like Armistice Day,
OL,16,FChristmas and Easter in future.
OL,18,FThe initial use, though, will see 164
OL,19,Fdouble-sided Union flags installed on
OL,20,Froads stretching from Worksop to
OL,21,FRuddington.
