OL,3,CReform council leader defends spending
OL,4,C#75k putting up Union flags
OL,6,FThe move follows a summer of debate
OL,7,Fover flags after the grassroots
OL,8,Fcampaign 'Operation Raise the Colours'
OL,9,Fwas launched in August 2025. The
OL,10,Fmovement saw calls for the prominent
OL,11,Fdisplay of the Union and English flags.
OL,13,FNottinghamshire County Council says it
OL,14,Fcurrently has 180 roadside locations
OL,15,Facross the area where it can display
OL,16,Fbanners from "time to time" to promote
OL,17,Fthe authority's activities - from
OL,18,Fservices like fostering to events like
OL,19,Fthe Nottinghamshire County Show.
