OL,3,CReform council leader defends spending
OL,4,C#75k putting up Union flags
OL,6,FThe authority says its #75,000
OL,7,Fspending relates to expanding this
OL,8,Fability to 82 other locations across
OL,9,FNottinghamshire.
OL,11,FBrackets to hold banners and flags in,
OL,12,Ftraffic management for the
OL,13,Finstallation of banners and flags, and
OL,14,Fa cherry picker to put them all up are
OL,15,Famong the items of spending aside from
OL,16,Fthe flags themselves.
OL,18,F"#75,000 is a lot of money that could
OL,19,Fbe used on council services."
