OL,3,CReform council leader defends spending
OL,4,C#75k putting up Union flags
OL,6,FCouncillor Penny Gowland, the leader
OL,7,Fof the Labour group at Nottinghamshire
OL,8,FCounty Council, said: "#75,000 is a
OL,9,Flot of money that could be used on
OL,10,Fcouncil services.
OL,12,F"If flags are about bringing us
OL,13,Ftogether, not dividing us, then I've
OL,14,Fgot no problem with it.
OL,16,F"But I think we should have the
OL,17,Fconfidence in our country not to put
OL,18,Fflags up everywhere."
