OL,3,CReform council leader defends spending
OL,4,C#75k putting up Union flags
OL,6,FCouncillor Gowland believed council
OL,7,Fbanners should only be installed "as
OL,8,Fneeded" rather than trying to "carpet
OL,9,Fthe whole county", adding on the flags
OL,10,Fin particular: "In some communities
OL,11,Fthey will see this as divisive, in
OL,12,Fsome communities they will see this as
OL,13,Fa joke, in some communities this will
OL,14,Fbe welcomed."
