OL,3,CReform council leader defends spending
OL,4,C#75k putting up Union flags
OL,6,FCouncillor Sam Smith, the Conservative
OL,7,Fleader of the opposition at the county
OL,8,Fcouncil, said: "I enjoy seeing flags
OL,9,Fflying on the lampposts but question
OL,10,Fwhy a council needs to spend money on
OL,11,Fputting them up when residents across
OL,12,Fthe county and country are doing it as
OL,13,Fpart of a grassroots, power to the
OL,14,Fpeople movement.
OL,16,F"We don't need to be spending on this
OL,17,Fwhen we can be spending money on
OL,18,Fprotecting taxpayer services like
OL,19,Flibraries, buses and youth services."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
