OL,3,CReform council leader defends spending
OL,4,C#75k putting up Union flags
OL,6,F"Initially the banners will be used
OL,7,Ffor displaying double-sided Union
OL,8,Fflags. Thereafter, they will be used
OL,9,Fto support other forthcoming events
OL,10,Flike Armistice Day, Christmas and
OL,11,FEaster events.
OL,13,F"The supports for the banners have
OL,14,Fbeen robustly tested and are fit for
OL,15,Fpurpose, hence they will last for many
OL,16,Fyears and represent good value for
OL,17,Fmoney. The safety of the public is
OL,18,Fforemost and it is something we will
OL,19,Fnot compromise on.
